data.description: PRICED TO SELL. Nestled amidst the tranquil beauty of Galena Forest, this single-level home on just over half an acre is a rare gem with the serenity of the forest and the convenience of city living. Just minutes away from shopping, freeways, and Lake Tahoe! This home features a cozy fireplace for warmth and ambiance, skylights and newer Milgard windows. A newer kitchen remodel and new insulation to keep you comfortable in all seasons. This home features a formal living room, a family room and a completed bonus/game room. The stunning forest views and a peaceful pond on this property offer a lifestyle that is truly unparalleled. Every corner exudes pride of ownership and attention to detail, ensuring a move-in-ready experience for the next owner.
